text: Sultan Duzelbayev is a Kazakhstani archer. He was born on 12 March 1994. Duzelbayev competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics.Sultan DuzelbayevSultan DUZELBAYEV == References == Category:Kazakhstani archers Category:Olympians for Kazakhstan Category:Living people Category:1994 births
